name: 少女たち（チュートリアル）

parameters:
\n<Aria>\C[24]Hehe... If you're like that, can you even do
your job? lol

\n<Girl B>Nooo, you can't hit the nail on the head like
that, Aria-chan! lol
\n<\N[3]>(Y-You... You dare to mock an adult...)

\n<Aria>\C[24]If the detective keeps attacking like that,
he'll be squeezed dry until he's completely
drained, you know? lol
\n<Aria>\C[24]Are you going to forcibly strip it off?

\n<Aria>\C[24]You're doing such things to weak little
girls? To top it off, you're even using violence,
you lolicon!

\n<Aria>\C[24]You're such a terrible criminal, aren't
you? Gotta report you to the police~♡

\n<Aria>\C[24]It's not violence, it's a sexual technique,
so it's safe♡

\n<Aria>\C[24]It's a win-win situation where neither of
us lose, and the uncle can feel good too♡ Isn't it
great♡
\n<\N[3]>Th-There's no way something like that can be done!

\n<Aria>\C[24]It's okay everyone. We don't need useless
toys that have no motivation. I'll give it to
you.
\n<Girl B>Ehh, I don't need it either...
\n<Girl A>It's fine as long as I'm aroused and can use it~
\n<\N[3]>Damn it...! This... is getting out of hand...!

\n<Aria>\C[24]Just so you know, if you think you can just
get off and it'll be over, you're in for a
surprise.

\n<Aria>\C[24]I can't go home until I play with everyone
and make sure everyone is satisfied, so there you
go~

\n<Aria>\C[24]That's exactly right. Didn't Luna-chan tell
you?

\n<Aria>\C[24]This is Luna-chan's game. Uncle doesn't
have any choices ♡

\n<Aria>\C[24]Uncle won't be able to leave here for the
rest of his life until he finishes playing with
Aria and Luna-chan ♡

\n<Aria>\C[24]If you want to keep playing forever, that's
fine with me~ ♡ I'll squeeze you dry over and over
again and make you mine ♡

\n<Aria>\C[24]You can keep having sex without going to
work forever ♡ Oh, is that what you wanted? LOL
\n<Girl B>No way, you're the worst kind of adult ♡

\n<\N[3]>(That's right... This is to break through this
situation...)

\n<\N[3]>(It's not a guilty feeling... And to teach these
children the fear of adults...)

\n<Aria>\C[24] ...Hehe... That's right, it's fine like
that ♡ Just make sure you don't wither away ♡
